Atlas 20mm (Call of duty Advanced Warfare Weapon)
Replaces Patriot
This weapon was suggested by Articfreezi
This is a Super Heavy Sniper Rifle (The heaviest one of all the heavy sniper rifles)

NOTE: weapon was supposed to be exactly the same, then i got creative and started editing things :P

Made to be used at long range

Horrible accuracy on hipfire 
But can have pinpoint accuracy when scoped (scope will constantly shake)
Insanely high damage
Slow reload
Slow firerate
High recoil
6 Round magazine
Regenerates 1 ammo every 4 seconds
Shots pierces enemies
Shots pierces shields
3 Seconds to enquip
2 Seconds to unenquip
-70% Movement speed
